This paper deals with completeness of logic programs, which is a topic in both logic (cs.LO) and programming languages (cs.PL). The use of the cut construct is specific to Prolog, which is a language commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) applications. The paper also discusses the pruning of search space, which is a topic in software engineering (cs.SE) and algorithms/data structures (cs.DS).
